                        <interp inst="t18400406-name-1400" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN GILBERT</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a shoemaker, and live at West-place, Turnham-green. I saw Wilkinson in a beer-shop—he offered me this drawer (<hi rend="italic">pro<lb></lb>ducing it</hi>), and asked if I would give him a pot of beer for it, which I did.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
